reviewText: i haven,t watch it yet but my friend said it was a good movie and i love ben stiller so i know it well be great

as a jim bruer fan i tried this movie and hung in for the whole film but i cant recommend it,wasnt funny,wasnt interesting, nothing good about it hopefully everyone got experience and hopefully future collaborations will be improved..i recommend jim bruers recent concert dvds to rent on netflix or blockbuster.com
